.subsection#user_details(data-title="Merchant Credentials")
  fieldset(data-title="MID Portal Login")
    .guide-text
      h3 It’s time to connect this account!
      p In order to start managing disputes, we'll need to connect to your account. Securely enter your login for your credit card processing portal, or upload a VAR sheet (sometimes called a tear sheet) to get started.
      p <strong>If you access your processor through a portal, please provide the following:</strong>
    .field
      label(for="mid_portal_url") The web address where you currently access data from your processor:
      input#mid_portal_url(type="text" name="mid_portal_url" placeholder="Processor Portal URL")
    .block
      .field
        label(for="mid_portal_username") A user name we can use to log in to the portal:
        input#mid_portal_username(type="text" name="mid_portal_username" placeholder="Portal Username")
      .field
        label(for="mid_portal_password") A password we can use to log in to the portal:
        input#mid_portal_password(type="text" name="mid_portal_password" placeholder="Portal Password")
    .guide-text.guide-text--alt
      span.guide-text__muted OR
      p If you’re unable to provide us with a login for your processor, we can connect manually using a VAR sheet, which can typically be found on the documents your received when the MID was first opened.
    .block
      label(for="mid_var_sheet") Upload VAR Sheet
      input#mid_var_sheet(type="file" name="mid_var_sheet" placeholder="VAR Sheet")
    .controls-wrapper
      button.review-subsection Review

